</listitem><listitem><para><bold>ğŸ“ˆ Extensible</bold> - Easy to add new MCUs and peripheral drivers</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>ğŸ”Œ Complete Coverage</bold> - 14+ peripheral interfaces for comprehensive hardware control</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
